        "ActionId": 23,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Amberia (Atiel)', 3: 'I am a deserter of the ARU. A \"sinner.\" Like that Forest Guard Diana, I am a descendant of those researchers in the past!', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 37,
        "ActionId": 1013,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Then why are you in Babylonia?', 3: '2000', 4: 'So is that why you\\'re familiar with that lab?', 5: '26'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 38,
        "ActionId": 2000,
        "NextActionId": 24,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500214', 3: '4'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 39,
        "ActionId": 24,
        "NextActionId": 25,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'She must have been part of those that escaped. Commandant, do you remember about the roadblocks outside of the lab?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 40,
        "ActionId": 25,
        "NextActionId": 1015,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Those were actually for stopping \"sinners\" from escaping. But even so, many people got out.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 41,
        "ActionId": 26,
        "NextActionId": 27,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Amberia (Atiel)', 3: '...Sharp eye, huh, 【kuroname】? But had I not done that, Lamia would\\'ve acquired the code first.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 42,
        "ActionId": 27,
        "NextActionId": 1015,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Amberia (Atiel)', 3: 'And I\\'d have lost my bargaining chip.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 43,
        "ActionId": 1015,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500209'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 44,
        "ActionId": 29,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Amberia (Atiel)', 3: '...I still remember what happened then. Angry mobs of people rushed into my home, tied me up and sent me to that dreadful building.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 45,
        "ActionId": 30,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Amberia (Atiel)', 3: 'Screams of agony could be heard day and night... Several of us managed to steal weapons from the guards. We thought we could find some small boat on the shore to escape on.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 46,
        "ActionId": 31,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Amberia (Atiel)', 3: 'In the end, I was the only one left. Everyone else was caught during their escape. I didn\\'t dare look back. I abandoned all of them, and I got out.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 47,
        "ActionId": 32,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Amberia (Atiel)', 3: 'But when I finally found freedom, I learned that something called the Punishing Virus is destroying the world. In order to live, I had to no choice but to become a Construct.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 48,
        "ActionId": 33,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Amberia (Atiel)', 3: 'And I fought, carefully, trying to stay alive in my operations... until I finally managed to seize this chance.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 49,
        "ActionId": 34,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Amberia (Atiel)', 3: '...The chance to return to this hellhole for vengeance!', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 50,
        "ActionId": 35,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Amberia (Atiel)', 3: 'Without the ARU, I no longer have to live in fear. If I can destroy them, the Ascendants will protect me.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 51,
        "ActionId": 36,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Amberia (Atiel)', 3: 'I want to live... No matter what!', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
